CONDITION: The following flat roof areas shown on plan nos.: K21 /08/05b; 08/09b; 08/12b; 08/13d; 08/14c; and 08/15c hereby approved shall not be used other than for essential maintenance or repair, or escape in case of emergency and shall not be used as amenity or sitting out spaces of any kind whatsoever:

a)	first floor flat roof of the side projection of Block A;
b)	the principal roof of Block A;
c)	second and third floor of the side projection of Block B; and
d)	the principal roof of Block B;

REASON: To prevent the overlooking of neighbouring habitable room windows in accordance with policy D3 H3 and H7 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002.
